welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Ocoee, the charming city known for its rich history and beautiful outdoor spaces. We invite you to explore and indulge in all that Ocoee has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Orlando Executive Airport serves both commercial and private aircraft.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Orlando Executive Airport caters to the needs of private jet owners and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Kissimmee Gateway Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Kissimmee Gateway Airport caters to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Wifi is available throughout the airport for free.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Orlando International Airport houses the check-in counters, baggage claim, and various shops and restaurants.

terminals.name: Terminal A
terminals.description: Terminal A is primarily used by domestic airlines and offers a variety of amenities and services for travelers.

terminals.name: Terminal B
terminals.description: Terminal B serves as the home for international airlines and features duty-free shops and other international services.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network throughout the terminal.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This is the main terminal of Orlando Sanford International Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal B
terminals.description: Terminal B is a newer addition to the airport, primarily used for international flights.

wifi.note: WiFi is available throughout the airport, but may require a password to access.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Leesburg Airport houses ticketing counters, baggage claim, and security checkpoints.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Leesburg Airport is used for private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's WiFi network for free.
